OL,3,CThirteen school building projects to
OL,4,Cprogress to construction stage
OL,6,FA number of building projects at
OL,7,Fschools in Northern Ireland are to
OL,8,Fprogress to the construction stage,
OL,9,Fthe Education Minister has announced.
OL,11,FPaul Givan said they include four new
OL,12,Fbuild projects and nine school
OL,13,Fenhancement projects.
OL,15,FHe made the annoucement at one of the
OL,16,Fschools set to benefit from a multi-
OL,17,Fmillion pounds investment, at Fairview
OL,18,FPrimary School in Ballyclare on
OL,19,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
