OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777539988
OL,3,CThirteen school building projects to
OL,4,Cprogress to construction stage
OL,6,FThe four major works projects are at
OL,7,FEnniskillen Royal Grammar School,
OL,8,FPriory Integrated College in Holywood,
OL,9,FDunclug College in Ballymena and St
OL,10,FMalachy's Primary School in Armagh.
OL,12,FThey will be delivered across a four-
OL,13,Fyear period, with a total capital
OL,14,Finvestment just over #130 million.
OL,16,FA further nine schools will move to
OL,17,Fconstruction on school enhancement
OL,18,Fprojects.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
