OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777539988
OL,3,CThirteen school building projects to
OL,4,Cprogress to construction stage
OL,6,FThese are Lurgan College, Greenhaw
OL,7,FPrimary School, Antrim Primary School,
OL,8,FFairview Primary School, Ballyclare
OL,9,FPrimary School, Chapel Road Primary
OL,10,FSchool, Our Lady of Lourdes Primary
OL,11,FSchool Belfast, St Bride's Primary
OL,12,FSchool Belfast and St Mary's Primary
OL,13,FSchool Newtownbutler.
OL,15,FSmallerscale refurbishment or
OL,16,Fextension works will take place at
OL,17,Fthese schools, representing a total
OL,18,Fcapital investment of just over #50
OL,19,Fmillion across a three-year period.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
