CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777539988
OL,3,CThirteen school building projects to
OL,4,Cprogress to construction stage
OL,6,FThe Education Minister said: "Many of
OL,7,Fthese projects have been in planning
OL,8,Ffor a significant number of years,
OL,9,Fserving schools that are in
OL,10,Fexceptionally poor condition that have
OL,11,Fseen little or no investment and now
OL,12,Furgently require replacement buildings.
OL,14,F"Whilst I continue to work to secure a
OL,15,FCapital Budget settlement that can
OL,16,Fdeliver the investment required for
OL,17,Four school estate, it is clear that
OL,18,Fthese schemes cannot continue to be
OL,19,Fheld back."
