CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777539988
OL,3,CThirteen school building projects to
OL,4,Cprogress to construction stage
OL,6,FPaul Givan added: "I believe this is a
OL,7,Fprudent approach to manage overall
OL,8,Fcapital expenditure by very carefully
OL,9,Fcontrolling the number of schemes
OL,10,Freleased to construction procurement,
OL,11,Fas part of a balanced portfolio of
OL,12,Fschemes aimed at addressing the
OL,13,Fdecades of underinvestment in our
OL,14,Fschool buildings."
